1. Ova *firma* se bavi proizvodnjom sportske opreme. (This *company* is engaged in the production of sports equipment.)
2. Prodao sam svoju *firmu* pre tri godine. (I sold my *business* three years ago.)
3. Moram da proverim dostupnost ove *firme* pre nego što naručim proizvode. (I need to check the availability of this *company* before I order products.)
4. Radim u jednoj *firmi* koja se bavi marketingom. (I work for a *company* that specializes in marketing.)
5. Naša *firma* je u procesu proširenja i otvaranja novih poslovnih jedinica. (Our *company* is in the process of expanding and opening new business units.)
6. Ova *firma* ima odličan ugled i reputaciju u poslovnom svetu. (This *company* has an excellent reputation in the business world.)
7. Koliko *firma* ima zaposlenih radnika? (How many *employees* does the company have?)
8. Naša *firma* je primila nagradu za inovaciju prošle godine. (Our *company* received an innovation award last year.)
9. Ova *firma* je vodeća u regionu po pitanju proizvodnje softvera za upravljanje skladištem. (This *company* is a leader in the region in terms of producing warehouse management software.)
10. Direktor ove *firme* je podneo ostavku nakon skandala koji je izbio u medijima. (The director of this *company* resigned after a scandal that broke out in the media.)